Class Subscriptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.spectator.atlas.impl.Subscriptions

  • public final class Subscriptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Model object for subscriptions payload coming from LWC service. Classes in this package are only intended for use internally within spectator. They may change at any time and without notice.

      • update

        public void update(java.util.Map<Subscription,java.lang.Long> subs,
                   long currentTime,
                   long expirationTime)
        Merge the subscriptions from this update into a map from subscriptions to expiration times.
        Parameters:
        subs - Existing subscriptions. The map value is the expiration time in millis since the epoch.
        currentTime - Current time to use for checking if entries are expired.
        expirationTime - Expiration time used for new and updated entries.
